{"tid":1580240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"改變藍絲！正式進入：「Facebook連儂牆計劃」","createTime":"2019-09-19T03:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T03:15:29.000Z","uid":48873,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2b30b49360eb2c381f57dda3f55f3c7dae94fa1b","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長話短說：成日話自己香港自己救, 請每人立即利用自己facebook做連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n做法：「每日都share反送中資訊」<br />\n目的： 打穿藍絲長輩同溫層！<br />\n</span><br />\n唔好話驚佢地見到會鬧，你facebook禁個share制先可以打破佢地嘅同溫層效應！比多d資訊去刺激佢地思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\">（係呀 佢地其實會諗野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個share，拯救一個生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長文：<br />\n<br />\n如果有日香港輸，一定係因為比班藍絲出賣。<br />\n如果我地要贏，一定要拎埋佢地嘅力量！<br />\n<br />\n天琦講過：「我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」<br />\n<br />\n我識身邊嘅人 <span style=\"color: gold;\">由黃轉藍好少，但藍轉淺黃</span>其實係易好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少Facebook, 老一輩真係好鍾意分享同留言。我今日搭巴士望住個藍絲呀嬸係到睇幫港出聲 又會睇留言 另外又會打長篇大論去覆藍絲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲媽媽最鍾意就係d煽情文章</span><br />\n例如「孩子！XXXXXX」<br />\n又或者「朋友！XXXXXX」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲叔叔最在乎就係錢同外國勢力</span><br />\n「反送中導致經濟/股市XXXXX」<br />\n「中美關係XXXXX」<br />\n<br />\n要打動佢地 變成淺黃，本人建議文宣小組係呢方面再努力d, 針對好Target audience. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實行：做法其實好簡單，由facebook share做起。</span></span><br />\n(老一輩仲沉迷緊）<br />\n<br />\n1. 平時Like文宣pages, 新聞pages<br />\n例子： 文宣很清楚開花這個責任<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105120017499651/posts/130618491616470?sfns=mo&lt;br&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105120017499651%2Fposts%2F130618491616470%3Fsfns%3Dmo%3Cbr%3E&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5T632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=0f79f885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105120017499651/posts/130618491616470?sfns=mo&lt;br&gt;</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n2. 見到認同嘅post, share+comment!!!<br />\n如果你有親人好藍&mdash;-&gt;可以唔加留言<br />\n如果親人淺藍&mdash;-&gt;加自己諗法 加強說服力 <br />\n<br />\n3. 高級間諜做法：入侵埋藍絲pages 留言逆轉風向<br />\np.s. 呢樣唔建議用自己ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍色媽媽們都已經做曬上面嘅野，仲分享勤力過你地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  網絡連儂牆快d建成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊急呼籲：<br />\n拯救身邊親人 幫佢地unlike垃圾page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nshare&amp;comment 多d facebook 文宣post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫親友Like吓立場新聞同連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設：每個人都拯救到一個親友，我地戰力又double了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多你一個share 多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d8e6e9b9fb56218139ca59fba773f2fd63a348","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"你班人係咪唔會睇政事台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8e85ea245dd45de1c3f7231cf8ced9acdb2f39","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拯救藍絲 人人有責"},{"pid":"6798b8ddcf0fe177df63acf8e925752dcecd736d","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"天琦講過：「我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」"},{"pid":"6150b657f998910a672aa0b5bda21de58b4acfc0","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"利用Facebook即時動態 可以令你想講嘅野放係最高位置<br />\n仲會成日碌碌吓係中間見到喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536dcda1a883053a3ac1ad44de693dbb89727b98","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"如果有日香港輸，一定係因為比班藍絲出賣。<br />\n如果我地要贏，一定要拎埋佢地嘅力量！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇呀 自己推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a8ae1bdf1216ae3d39aa6aca109c369171d428","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"IG story都係唔錯嘅宣傳渠道<br />\n提醒你嘅港豬朋友 每日有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b8b98867044a59083a095fb0881ab09dff2a01","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠招各位加入網絡打手"},{"pid":"602b0ece3dec333a64f32f356b769adfa01064b3","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"藍絲們，<br />\n如果有天，你去醫院割盲腸，但腎臟不見了<br />\n《不要害怕，是你爭取的》<br />\n<br />\n如果有天，你的子女飲奶粉變了大頭嬰<br />\n《不要害怕，是你爭取的》<br />\n<br />\n如果有天，你拖狗散步，<br />\n警察說不能養大狗 要抓走牠<br />\n《不要害怕，是你爭取的》<br />\n<br />\n如果有天，你投資生意被騙了 還被抓去坐牢<br />\n《不要害怕，是你爭取的》<br />\n<br />\n如果有天，你想投訴政府，<br />\n但投訴無門還被人打一身<br />\n《不要害怕，是你爭取的》<br />\n<br />\n如果有天，香港再沒有言論自由，<br />\n真正變成了大陸模式<br />\n藍絲們 《不要害怕，全都是你們爭取的！！》<br />\n<br />\n不要跟我說不會，這裡是香港這些廢話！<br />\n是你們他媽的努力去爭取把香港變成大陸的！！！<br />\n<br />\n你們只看到眼前利益，看不到將來，<br />\n也不會去想將來，真的為你們感到可悲！"},{"pid":"45ececcc77c764a5588091a035644457d16e34d4","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d76df3fb6c8b30f8c1a0b9919ef13cd67eaa85","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbc992f3d56554f03864aa8ce73045924ec24b4","tid":1580240,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6527c6f468ab2ef0b5bdf9d87cffa1979aab180","tid":1580240,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":